ooping six bronze medals in total.READ MORE:England could be about to shoot themselves in the foot with next manager search after Gareth Southgate exitShe was given a CBE to recognise her achievements back in 2013.Speaking before her decision to withdraw from the Olympics, Dujardin had said she was looking forward to potentially making history out in France.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1869, \"end\": 1876, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valegro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Valegro\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valegro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valegro\"}, {\"begin\": 1943, \"end\": 1946, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999913598, \"rank\": 8.64967442184812e-11, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2012, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999904716666262, \"rank\": 9.528424175662821e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2065, \"end\": 2072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9959164831046696, \"rank\": 0.002759481563336674, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/England_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2188, \"end\": 2191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_the_British_Empire\", \"score\": 0.9999999990930064, \"rank\": 9.06881249538163e-10, \"text\": \"CBE\", \"types\": [], \"wi