aking her proud.\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3363, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3264, \"end\": 3282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want for her, one day, to look back and go: 'That's my mummy and how cool was that that she was there competing at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And, I was there to watch.'\\\"\", \"from\": 3495, \"to\": 3523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dujardin is Britain's second-most decorated female Olympian.\", \"from\": 3525, \"to\": 3585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3537, \"end\": 3544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"score\": 0.8003505741601429, \"rank\": 0.2494521781139064, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain\"}, {\"begin\": 3576, \"end\": 3584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999998093546947, \"rank\": 1.9064523857023323e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Announcing the news, she said in a statement: \\\"A video has emerged from four years ago which shows me making an error of judgement during a coaching session.\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024: Charlotte Dujardin has withdrawn from the games in Paris  GETTY  \\\"Understandably, the International Federation for Equestrian Sports (FEI) is investigating and I have made the decision to withdraw from all competition - including the Paris Olympics - while